revision.text: ==English== ===Etymology=== From {{bor|en|kok|शागोती}}, {{m|kok|सागुती}}. ===Noun=== {{en-noun|-}} # A [[Goan]] [[curry]] with a complex mixture of [[spice]]s including white [[poppy]] seeds and large dried red [[chili]]s, usually prepared with [[chicken]] or [[lamb]]. ====Alternative forms==== * {{l|en|xacutti}}
